      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "3c97529d9b3e2cc2d53d2bd4a6d7984c",
      "text": "# Reception"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "e82a712da10da162c49d48274c29c3f4",
      "text": "<table class=\"metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-content\" role=\"presentation\"><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\">50x40px ([[File:Crystal Clear app kedit.svg]])</div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><span class=\"mbox-text-span\">This article may need to be '''rewritten entirely''' to comply with Wikipedia's quality standards ([[Wikipedia:Manual of Style]]), as section.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> [//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=GNU_General_Public_License&action=edit You can help]. The discussion page ([[Talk:GNU General Public License]]) may contain suggestions.</span>  <small>''(January 2013)''</small><span class=\"hide-when-compact\"></span></span></td></tr></table>[[Category:Wikipedia articles needing rewrite from January 2013]]"
